Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.54,OPp2,,0,0,0,,(Ay-ya-ya!)
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.54,0:04:02.80,OP,,0,0,0,,For heated battles, I choose you! (For heated battles, I choose you!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:04:02.80,OPp2,,0,0,0,,For heated battles, I choose you! (For heated battles, I choose you!)
