Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:07.13,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Yo! Champ in the making! Now, let’s keep up the enthusiasm today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:10.85,OPED,,0,0,0,,Get them, get them! (Get them, get them!) Now, let’s keep making friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:12.39,OPED,,0,0,0,,No Super Ball, Hyper Ball, or even a Master Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.60,OPED,,0,0,0,,can capture your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:18.27,OPED,,0,0,0,,But if we dance together, things’ll keep getting more lively!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:22.15,OPED,,0,0,0,,Normal, Fighting, Poison, Ground, Flying, Bug, Rock, Ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:24.03,OPED,,0,0,0,,Steel, Fire, Water, Electric, Grass, Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:25.94,OPED,,0,0,0,,Psychic, Dragon, Dark, Fairy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.57,OPED,,0,0,0,,Whether they’re evolved or not, get them all together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:33.58,OPED,,0,0,0,,and strike a full power pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:37.33,OPED,,0,0,0,,Freezing Ice will make you shiver with cold
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:41.08,OPED,,0,0,0,,Toxic Poison will eat away at your body
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:44.84,OPED,,0,0,0,,A Psychic will leave you dizzy and confused
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:48.76,OPED,,0,0,0,,Do things the Normal way, because simplicity is best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:55.93,OPED,,0,0,0,,I’m glad I met you, I’m really glad I chose you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:03.36,OPED,,0,0,0,,Once we’ve stuffed plenty of memories into our pockets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:10.91,OPED,,0,0,0,,Let’s walk while holding hands, and stay together even through painful times
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:20.54,OPED,,0,0,0,,So that we can meet here again once we’ve grown up
